    "#  Evolutionary Algorithm for Cardiac Health Classification\n",
    "**Bioinformatics Portfolio Project**\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook uses a **Genetic Algorithm (GA)** to evolve the hyperparameters and feature selection of a machine learning classifier that distinguishes **healthy vs. unhealthy** patients from echocardiogram/cardiac data.\n",
    "\n",
    "### Pipeline Overview\n",
    "1. Load cardiac dataset (from Google Drive or UCI fallback)\n",
    "2. Preprocess & split healthy/unhealthy\n",
    "3. Define a GA to evolve: feature subsets + model hyperparameters\n",
    "4. Evaluate fitness via cross-validated AUC\n",
    "5. Visualize evolution and final classifier performance\n",
    "\n",
    "**Evolutionary Strategy:** Each *individual* in the population encodes:\n",
    "- Which features to include (binary gene mask)\n",
    "- ML hyperparameters (e.g., max_depth, n_estimators, learning_rate)"
